    <item>
      <title>HDFC 正与全球银行洽谈出售 10 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/hdfc-in-talks-with-global-banks-to-offload-1-billion-in-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度最大的私营部门贷款机构 HDFC 银行有限公司 (HDFC Bank Ltd.) 正在与几家全球银行进行谈判，以出售高达 840 亿卢比（10 亿美元）的贷款，从而减少其信贷规模，使其与存款规模更加一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/hdfc-in-talks-with-global-banks-to-offload-1-billion-in-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:32:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IEEFA 称欧洲液化天然气产量达到峰值，搁浅资产风险加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/europe-at-peak-lng-heightens-risk-of-stranded-assets-ieefa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家能源智库表示，欧洲液化天然气消费量可能已达到峰值，但仍在继续建设进口终端和相关基础设施，这增加了这些工程闲置并成为搁浅资产的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/europe-at-peak-lng-heightens-risk-of-stranded-assets-ieefa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚将在欧洲央行和美联储采取行动前恢复宽松政策：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/serbia-to-resume-easing-ahead-of-ecb-fed-moves-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于塞尔维亚央行预测通胀将进一步放缓且欧洲和美国政策制定者预计将降低利率，塞尔维亚准备在上个月暂停货币宽松政策后恢复货币宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/serbia-to-resume-easing-ahead-of-ecb-fed-moves-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将降息但仍对未来路径持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/ecb-interest-rates-decision-lagarde-to-cut-but-stay-guarded-on-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将再次下调利率，但由于通胀尚未完全得到抑制，其对进一步行动的速度和程度仍守口如瓶。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/ecb-interest-rates-decision-lagarde-to-cut-but-stay-guarded-on-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求国内汽车制造商将关键电动汽车技术留在国内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/china-asks-carmakers-to-keep-key-ev-technology-at-home-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，中国强烈建议国内汽车制造商确保先进的电动汽车技术留在国内，即使这些公司在全球各地建厂。丹尼·李在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/china-asks-carmakers-to-keep-key-ev-technology-at-home-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 03:35:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
