      <title>东南亚股票为何吸引投资者？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/why-are-southeast-asian-stocks-attracting-investors-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛亚太区首席股票策略师 Timothy Moe 讨论了美联储政策、对亚洲市场的影响以及他认为该地区的机会。他在“彭博：中国秀”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/why-are-southeast-asian-stocks-attracting-investors-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 03:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小型 IPO 蓬勃发展之际，印度考虑制定新规以遏制风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/india-said-to-mull-new-rules-to-curb-risks-as-tiny-ipos-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据参与讨论的人士透露，印度证券监管机构正在考虑对小型股公司上市实施更严格的监管，包括监控其资金使用情况并对商业银行家实施更严格的尽职调查准则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/india-said-to-mull-new-rules-to-curb-risks-as-tiny-ipos-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 03:29:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
