    <item>
      <title>据称澳新银行将重启出售雅加达上市银行 Panin 股份的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/anz-is-said-to-revive-plan-to-sell-stake-in-jakarta-listed-bank-panin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，澳新银行集团控股有限公司正考虑重启出售其在印尼央行银行股份的计划，因该银行希望减少其长期持有的一些亚洲资产的头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/anz-is-said-to-revive-plan-to-sell-stake-in-jakarta-listed-bank-panin</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 09:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
